OVERVIEW
--------

DBI::Wrap is a simple object oriented wrapper around DBI.  It provides
methods for most SQL queries.  SQL query clauses and parameters are
defined by named parameters to the methods.  See the POD document for
DBI::Wrap for more documentation.

INSTALLATION
------------

The latest version of DBI::Wrap can be obtained from:

  http://search.cpan.org/author/EMRYS/DBI-Wrap-1.00

To install DBI::Wrap

  gunzip DBI-Wrap-1.00.tar.gz
  tar xvf DBI-Wrap-1.00.tar
  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install
